title: Jenkins and Jonez - Joe Burrow Is HIM and Ben Simmons Is…Maybe Also Him?

description:
The guys discuss the horrible new Washington Football Team name, Mike coming all the way around on Ben Simmons, how Joe Burrow is the first athlete whose old tweets somehow make him *cooler*, the details of the Brian Flores story, Rihanna’s pregnancy news, and much more.
